        <p class="mt-7 max-w-3xl text-xl text-cyan-100">This battlecard compares Postscript and Brevo as parts of a revenue operating system — not isolated badges. We stress-tested welcome, cart recovery, post-purchase, and winback, then scored stack fit, Shopify context, execution burden, and margin-aware measurement.</p>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-300">Postscript (SMS marketing) vs Brevo (Email, SMS & transactional). Ratings: ★ 4.7/5 vs ★ 4.5/5. Sequenzy remains the lifecycle layer we recommend when coordination — not feature count — is the bottleneck.</p>
